      • debugPrintComponentTree

        public static void debugPrintComponentTree(java.io.PrintWriter pr,
                           Component com)
        Prints the component tree to a PrintWriter. This can be used for debugging. Any exceptions occurring while processing the tree will be output into the given PrintWrier.
        Parameters:
        pr - The PrintWriter for output, must not be null
        com - The top-level Component where the tree will start, must not be null
